## Evaluation Summary (generated file)

This file is generated by `python -m eval.run_eval`.

If you are seeing EM/F1 values here that do not match your current `eval/dataset.jsonl`, regenerate results with:

```bash
python -m eval.run_eval --dataset eval/dataset.jsonl --out results/results.csv --only-public --methods llm_only,rag_similarity,rag_mmr,ours --skip-judge
```

If Cohere returns `429 TooManyRequestsError` (Trial key quota), you must wait for quota reset or use a Production key.
